data.description: From the inviting living room anchored by a gas fireplace, walk across the Brazilian Cherry HW floors, through french doors, to the kitchen flooded by natural daylight.  Look out over the farm sink and granite countertops to the over-sized rear yard accessible through dual patio doors.   Come see the charming and elegant details that will make you proud to call this well-maintained Center Hall Colonial home located on a quiet, tree lined street.
